The Nike Kobe Mamba Mentality Los Angeles Lakers City Edition Swingman Jersey (FW23) Black was one of the many pieces of apparel that was featured in this collection.




The majority of this jersey was black, and it featured a snakeskin-embossed pattern on it in tribute to Kobe's "Black Mamba" nickname. In our opinion, though, the best thing about this jersey was that it included each of the numbers that Kobe wore when he played with the Lakers over two decades. product: Nike Kobe Mamba Mentality Los Angeles Lakers City Edition Swingman Jersey (FW23) BlackLowest AskCA$153
product_name: Nike Kobe Mamba Mentality Los Angeles Lakers City Edition Swingman Jersey (FW23)
product_description:
Nike's Mamba Mentality apparel collection was created to celebrate all the things that made Kobe Bryant such a special player throughout his NBA career. The Nike Kobe Mamba Mentality Los Angeles Lakers City Edition Swingman Jersey (FW23) Black was one of the many pieces of apparel that was featured in this collection.




The majority of this jersey was black, and it featured a snakeskin-embossed pattern on it in tribute to Kobe's "Black Mamba" nickname. It also had smaller hints of the Los Angeles Lakers' gold and purple colors, and it was made of a moisture-wicking fabric to make it lightweight when worn on the basketball court.




In our opinion, though, the best thing about this jersey was that it included each of the numbers that Kobe wore when he played with the Lakers over two decades. The #8 that he wore at the start of his career was on the front, while the #24 that he wore towards the end of it was on the back. The Nike Kobe Mamba Mentality Los Angeles Lakers City Edition Swingman Jersey (FW23) Black was released on December 27, 2023, and it initially retailed for $120.

product: Swatch x Omega Bioceramic Moonswatch Mission To Moonphase SnoopyLowest AskCA$473
product_name: Swatch x Omega Bioceramic Moonswatch Mission To Moonphase Snoopy
product_description:
The Swatch x Omega Bioceramic Moonswatch Mission To Moonphase Snoopy Black, a fusion of innovation and style. Crafted with meticulous attention to detail, this timepiece boasts a sleek IO ceramic case, crown, and pushers, complemented by a durable VELCRO© strap for ultimate comfort.



Distinguished by its striking design elements, the chronograph features white subdial hands and a tachymeter-scaled bezel against a contrasting black background. But what truly sets this model apart is its captivating black moon phase function, evoking a sense of poetic allure. At the heart of the design lies Snoopy, NASA’s beloved safety ambassador, depicted reclining on the moon within the subdial set at 2 o’clock. Under UV light, a hidden quote from a Snoopy comic strip emerges, nestled among crescent moons and stars, adding an element of whimsy and discovery.



For added functionality, the indexes, hour and minute hands, and the tip of the chronograph seconds hand are adorned with Grade A Super-LumiNova®, ensuring clear visibility even in low-light conditions.



Experience the perfect fusion of form and function with the Swatch x Omega Bioceramic Moonswatch Mission To Moonphase Snoopy Black — released April 8, 2024 with a retail price of $310.

product: Denim Tears Cotton Wreath Hoodie Black MonochromeLowest AskCA$360
product_description:
The Denim Tears Cotton Wreath Hoodie Black Monochrome is a 100% cotton pullover hooded sweatshirt in Black, featuring a kangaroo front pocket. The sweatshirt fabric features a floral wreath print, rendered in black puff ink screen printing, which appears all over the body of the sweatshirt. Denim Tears branding appears on the woven label inside the collar.




Denim Tears was founded by designer Tremaine Emory in 2019. Each collection is designed to tell a story unveiling the African Diaspora. For the brand’s innovative work, Denim Tears’ has achieved a place within The Metropolitan Museum of Art Costume Institute’s permanent collection in New York, a major honor in fashion.




Our experts feel that the best feature of the Wreath Hoodie is its monochrome print, which subtly identifies Denim Tears without the use of visual branding. The Denim Tears Cotton Wreath Hoodie Black Monochrome released on March 15, 2024, and retailed at $210.
